high_descs: Turn right to walk to the sink.
Pick up the middle knife in the sink.
Turn and walk to the opposite counter, where the potato is.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Turn left to walk to the toaster.
Set the knife down in front of the toaster.
Walk back to the counter where the potato is.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the potato in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn right to walk to the toaster.
Set the potato down on the counter next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of potato in the microwave to set in front of the toaster.

high_descs: go to the sink

take the knife to the island where the bread loaf is
cut the potato on the counter
take the knife to the toaster on the counter
lay the knife in front of the toaster on the counter
go to the island
pick up a potato slice
take the slice to the microwave
put the slice in the microwave, cook, then remove
take the cooked potato slice to the counter near the toaster
set the slice to the left of the knife on the counter

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the tomato in the sink.
Turn around and head to the counter with the bread on it.
Cut the potato on the counter.
Turn left and head to the toaster.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the toaster.
Turn around and go back to the counter with the sliced potato.
